snippet.title: Best VGM 687 - Magna Carta : Tears of Blood - The Poet of Efort
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PS2
Magna Carta : Tears of Blood (2005)
The Poet of Efort
Sung-Woon Jang
